snippet.title: Judas Priest - Firepower (Cover)
snippet.description:
I really admire the band since I was kid, they are still mighty and hope they will stay forever.

We reinterpreted the Sentinel of Judas Priest two years ago with modern approach and I guess people loved our job. 

A month ago, I listened to their new album and I liked it very much so I suggested Leo to make something like we did on the Sentinel. And here we are...

By the way, I would like to introduce to you guys, my new great lead guitarist ‘WEE’, we are going to make lots of cover together so on, maybe twice a month. Hopefully, I can handle my schedule.

Have a nice one, folks. Peace!

Siegfried Song (Symmetric Chaos, South Korea) - Lead Vocals, Harmony Vocals, Video Editing
Leo Peña (Jotun Studio, Spain) - Rhythm Guitars, Bass, Drum Programming, Mixing, Mastering, Video Editing
'WEE' SungHun (MuTrickster, South Korea) - Lead Guitars
